      protected void defineAttribute​(String attr, Object value, boolean advertise)

    • setAttribute

      protected void setAttribute​(String attr, Object value)
      Change the value of an attribute. The attribute must exist. The attribute's value cannot be null and its class must equal that of the previous value. The attribute listeners are called when an attribute is changed.
